(Śikṣāsamuccaya 7–8)

iti | śamathamāhātmyaṃ tu yathāvasaram ihaiva kathayiṣyate.

<commentary>suniścitaṃ saṃdehaviparyāsarahitam. suprasannaṃ sadā prītisaumanasyabahulam. dhīram acañcalam. ādaraḥ kathita eva. gauravaṃ ārādhyeṣu cittasya namratā. tābhyāṃ saha vartate. salajjaṃ pūrvavat. sabhayaṃ skhalitam ālokya bhītam. śāntaṃ saṃyatendriyam, sattvārādhanayatnavat.</commentary>

yad ekasya rucijanakaṃ tad anyasya viparītam. anyonyaviruddhābhiḥ pṛthagjanecchābhirakheditam avipratisāri. katham?